The paper deals with the problem of recognizing handwritten mathematical expressions, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The proposed method utilizes attention mechanisms, which are commonly used in natural language processing (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
